{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Just before he is leaving he says, I had a change of heart.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going to be nice to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm going to let you go into the building and sleep, to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We all went into the building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At the crack of dawn, as light started to-- the next day, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] somebody was saying, oh, my God, look at all our wives, and our sisters, and our brothers approaching the building.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They brought everybody that they didn't take the day before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the younger siblings, the women, they brought them to the place that all the men were assembled the day before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of chaos started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They let us out of the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Husbands ran to find their wives, to find their children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Children were looking for their mother and father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And children were hollering, daddy, mommy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there were a lot of daddys and mommy calls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know whether all families really got reunited again or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the way, the women and children were also told when they were told to assemble that they can carry everything-- just anything that they can carry on their back, no more.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People grabbed blankets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "People grabbed food, whatever was important to-- to the individual.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some people, things were more important to others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Whatever they thought was important, they-- that's what they had as hand baggage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When we were all together, they made all the men go up front and all the women follow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there-- we're being told to march.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
